Dokumentation:

The imports for TensorFlow.js import Movenet a PoseDetection system

"Confidence-Treshold":
Each Keypoint has a score.
Scores range between 0.0 to 1.0 the higher the score the more the posedetection system is shure that the Keypoints is really in the right place
the  Treshold itself is just here so that the model ignores bad detectcions.

CameraFeed:
It is basically the all encompassing method that we use for the model.

